"use strict";(self.webpackChunkdoc_website=self.webpackChunkdoc_website||[]).push([[525],{210:e=>{e.exports=JSON.parse('{"blogPosts":[{"id":"how-to-trade","metadata":{"permalink":"/tr/blog/how-to-trade","source":"@site/i18n/tr/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/how-to-trade.md","title":"ArithFi\'nin Lightning Trade \xf6zelli\u011fini ilk ticaretiniz i\xe7in nas\u0131l kullan\u0131rs\u0131n\u0131z?","description":"ArithFi, merkezi olmayan bir t\xfcrevler borsas\u0131d\u0131r ve piyasa yap\u0131c\u0131lar\u0131 ile LP\'leri ortadan kald\u0131r\u0131r. ArithFi \xfczerinde yapaca\u011f\u0131n\u0131z ticaret, kullan\u0131c\u0131lara h\u0131zl\u0131, kolay, g\xfcvenli ve \u015feffaf bir ticaret deneyimi sunar. 1-50X kald\u0131ra\xe7 kullanarak, Lightning Trade stratejinizi olu\u015fturmak i\xe7in Layer 2\'ye depozito yap\u0131n. Layer 2\'den fonlar\u0131n\u0131z\u0131 \xe7ekmek i\xe7in bekleme s\xfcresi gerekmez ve gelecekteki kazan\xe7lar\u0131n\u0131z ArithFi hesab\u0131n\u0131za aktar\u0131l\u0131r.","date":"2023-09-25T06:04:36.000Z","formattedDate":"25 Eyl\xfcl 2023","tags":[{"label":"guild","permalink":"/tr/blog/tags/guild"}],"readingTime":1.635,"hasTruncateMarker":false,"authors":[],"frontMatter":{"slug":"how-to-trade","title":"ArithFi\'nin Lightning Trade \xf6zelli\u011fini ilk ticaretiniz i\xe7in nas\u0131l kullan\u0131rs\u0131n\u0131z?","tags":["guild"]},"nextItem":{"title":"How to use copy trading feature on ArithFi?","permalink":"/tr/blog/guildline"}},"content":"ArithFi, merkezi olmayan bir t\xfcrevler borsas\u0131d\u0131r ve piyasa yap\u0131c\u0131lar\u0131 ile LP\'leri ortadan kald\u0131r\u0131r. ArithFi \xfczerinde yapaca\u011f\u0131n\u0131z ticaret, kullan\u0131c\u0131lara h\u0131zl\u0131, kolay, g\xfcvenli ve \u015feffaf bir ticaret deneyimi sunar. 1-50X kald\u0131ra\xe7 kullanarak, Lightning Trade stratejinizi olu\u015fturmak i\xe7in Layer 2\'ye depozito yap\u0131n. Layer 2\'den fonlar\u0131n\u0131z\u0131 \xe7ekmek i\xe7in bekleme s\xfcresi gerekmez ve gelecekteki kazan\xe7lar\u0131n\u0131z ArithFi hesab\u0131n\u0131za aktar\u0131l\u0131r.\\n\\n- Daha d\xfc\u015f\xfck maliyet - T\xfcm ticaret s\xfcreci boyunca gaz \xfccreti al\u0131nmaz.\\n- Daha d\xfczg\xfcn - Lightning trading ile sorunsuz pozisyon a\xe7\u0131l\u0131\u015f\u0131 yap\u0131n.\\n- A\xe7\u0131k ve \u015feffaf - \u0130\u015flemler h\u0131zl\u0131 bir \u015fekilde ger\xe7ekle\u015ftirilir ve dakikalar i\xe7inde blockchain \xfczerinde onaylan\u0131r.\\n\\n**ArithFi\'de Lightning Trade deneyiminizi bu d\xf6rt kolay ad\u0131m\u0131 izleyerek ba\u015flat\u0131n.**\\n\\nAd\u0131m 1: C\xfczdan\u0131n\u0131z\u0131 ba\u011flay\u0131n ve hesab\u0131n\u0131z\u0131 do\u011frulay\u0131n.\\n\\nAd\u0131m 2: ArithFi hesab\u0131n\u0131za depozito yap\u0131n.\\n\\nAd\u0131m 3: Ticarete ba\u015flay\u0131n.\\n\\n## Ad\u0131m 1: C\xfczdan\u0131n\u0131z\u0131 ba\u011flay\u0131n ve hesab\u0131n\u0131z\u0131 do\u011frulay\u0131n.\\n\\n(1) C\xfczdan\u0131n\u0131z\u0131 ba\u011flamak i\xe7in \\"C\xfczdan Ba\u011fla\\" d\xfc\u011fmesine t\u0131klay\u0131n.\\n\\n![](https://bafybeicp5kgnfe7q6vtc6jlprv33setne7hmdwhwthop2juj7j3e257df4.ipfs.nftstorage.link/11.png)\\n\\n(2) Adresinizi do\u011frulamak i\xe7in \\"\u0130stek G\xf6nder\\" d\xfc\u011fmesine t\u0131klay\u0131n.\\n\\n![](https://bafybeicp5kgnfe7q6vtc6jlprv33setne7hmdwhwthop2juj7j3e257df4.ipfs.nftstorage.link/22.png)\\n\\n## Ad\u0131m 2: ArithFi hesab\u0131n\u0131za depozito yap\u0131n.\\n\\n(1) ArithFi hesab\u0131n\u0131za depozito yapmak i\xe7in \\"Hesap\\" ve \\"Depozito\\" se\xe7eneklerine t\u0131klay\u0131n.\\n\\n![](https://bafybeicp5kgnfe7q6vtc6jlprv33setne7hmdwhwthop2juj7j3e257df4.ipfs.nftstorage.link/33.png)\\n\\n(2) Hesap depozito ve \xe7ekim kay\u0131tlar\u0131n\u0131z\u0131 g\xf6r\xfcnt\xfclemek i\xe7in \\"Genel Bak\u0131\u015f\\" se\xe7ene\u011fine t\u0131klay\u0131n.\\n\\n![](https://bafybeicp5kgnfe7q6vtc6jlprv33setne7hmdwhwthop2juj7j3e257df4.ipfs.nftstorage.link/44.png)\\n\\n**Not:**\\n\\n- Depozito i\u015flemleri ArithFi (ATF), USDT ve BNB \xf6deme y\xf6ntemlerini kabul eder. Sistem bunlar\u0131 hemen ArithFi hesab\u0131n\u0131za ATF\'ye d\xf6n\xfc\u015ft\xfcr\xfcr.\\n- Depozito i\u015flemlerinde hizmet \xfccreti al\u0131nmaz, sadece k\xfc\xe7\xfck bir gaz \xfccreti al\u0131n\u0131r.\\n- \xc7ekim i\u015flemleri yaln\u0131zca ATF ile desteklenir ve her \xe7ekim i\u015flemi i\xe7in 15 ATF hizmet \xfccreti al\u0131n\u0131r.\\n\\n## Ad\u0131m 3: Ticarete ba\u015flay\u0131n.\\n\\n(1) Vadeli i\u015flemler ticaret \xe7iftini se\xe7in, pozisyon parametrelerini doldurun ve \\"Uzun Pozisyon A\xe7\\" d\xfc\u011fmesine t\u0131klayarak pozisyonunuzu a\xe7\u0131n.\\n\\n![](https://bafybeicp5kgnfe7q6vtc6jlprv33setne7hmdwhwthop2juj7j3e257df4.ipfs.nftstorage.link/55.png)\\n\\n(2) Pozisyonlar\u0131n\u0131z\u0131 kapatma, teminat ekleme, Kar Al ve Zarar Durdur fiyatlar\u0131n\u0131 belirleme ve payla\u015fma gibi i\u015flemleri yapmak i\xe7in alt k\u0131s\u0131mda sipari\u015flerinizi g\xf6r\xfcnt\xfcleyebilir ve y\xf6netebilirsiniz.\\n\\n![](https://bafybeicp5kgnfe7q6vtc6jlprv33setne7hmdwhwthop2juj7j3e257df4.ipfs.nftstorage.link/66.png)\\n\\n**Not:**\\n\\n- Pozisyon a\xe7ma ve kapatma i\u015flemleri pozisyonun %0.05\'i kadar hizmet \xfccretini i\xe7erirken, teminat ekleme i\u015flemi hizmet \xfccreti gerektirmez.\\n\\n- G\xfcnl\xfck sabit baz faiz oranlar\u0131 \u2460 BTC/USDT, ETH/USDT: %0.03\\n\\n  \u2461 MATIC/USDT, ADA/USDT, DOGE/USDT, XRP/USDT,BNB/USDT: %0.05\\n\\n## Ad\u0131m 4: Karlar\u0131n\u0131z\u0131 g\xf6r\xfcnt\xfcleyin.\\n\\n(1) \\"Hesap\\" \xfczerine t\u0131klay\u0131n ve bu sayfada ticaret performans\u0131n\u0131z\u0131 ve kar\u0131n\u0131z\u0131 g\xf6r\xfcnt\xfcleyin.\\n\\n![](https://bafybeicp5kgnfe7q6vtc6jlprv33setne7hmdwhwthop2juj7j3e257df4.ipfs.nftstorage.link/77.png)"},{"id":"guildline","metadata":{"permalink":"/tr/blog/guildline","source":"@site/blog/guildline.md","title":"How to use copy trading feature on ArithFi?","description":"A seamless futures trading experience may be had anytime, anywhere by using ArithFi copy trading service. Follow the trading strategies of the top traders around the world in the trader\'s square with just a single click. Here is the beginners\' guide on ArithFi Copy Trading service.","date":"2023-09-23T09:25:27.000Z","formattedDate":"23 Eyl\xfcl 2023","tags":[{"label":"guild","permalink":"/tr/blog/tags/guild"}],"readingTime":0.905,"hasTruncateMarker":false,"authors":[],"frontMatter":{"slug":"guildline","title":"How to use copy trading feature on ArithFi?","tags":["guild"]},"prevItem":{"title":"ArithFi\'nin Lightning Trade \xf6zelli\u011fini ilk ticaretiniz i\xe7in nas\u0131l kullan\u0131rs\u0131n\u0131z?","permalink":"/tr/blog/how-to-trade"}},"content":"A seamless futures trading experience may be had anytime, anywhere by using ArithFi copy trading service. Follow the trading strategies of the top traders around the world in the trader\'s square with just a single click. Here is the beginners\' guide on ArithFi Copy Trading service.\\n\\n1. ##### Visit https://arithfi.com/#/copy on your wallet browser or PC and Connect your wallet.\\n\\n   ###### ![111.png](https://bafybeibixmvl5uy7yanoqd24ybpozioj3omynxxvmaqdpjdcs2bpfdph3y.ipfs.nftstorage.link/111.png)\\n\\n2. ##### Link your wallet and click \\"Send request\\" to verify your ownership.\\n\\n   ###### ![222.png](https://bafybeibixmvl5uy7yanoqd24ybpozioj3omynxxvmaqdpjdcs2bpfdph3y.ipfs.nftstorage.link/222.png)\\n\\n3. ##### Click \\"Account\\" and then click \\"Deposit\\" for your ArithFi Lightning Trade account.\\n\\n   ![44.jpg](https://bafybeibixmvl5uy7yanoqd24ybpozioj3omynxxvmaqdpjdcs2bpfdph3y.ipfs.nftstorage.link/333.png)\\n\\n4. ##### Go on copy trading feature and select the trader by clicking \\"Copy\\".\\n\\n   ###### ![333.png](https://bafybeibixmvl5uy7yanoqd24ybpozioj3omynxxvmaqdpjdcs2bpfdph3y.ipfs.nftstorage.link/444.png)\\n\\n5. ##### Setting copy trading investment for the trader\\n\\n   Set the total investment amount and single investment amount of your copy trader.\\n\\n   ###### ![555.png](https://bafybeibixmvl5uy7yanoqd24ybpozioj3omynxxvmaqdpjdcs2bpfdph3y.ipfs.nftstorage.link/555.png)\\n\\n6. ##### View your copy trader\\n\\n   Back to the Copy home page and click \\"My Copies\\" to view your copy trading details.\\n\\n   ###### ![777.png](https://bafybeibixmvl5uy7yanoqd24ybpozioj3omynxxvmaqdpjdcs2bpfdph3y.ipfs.nftstorage.link/666.png)\\n\\n7. ##### Click \\"My Traders\\" to check your followed trader.\\n\\n   You can choose to stop copying the trader or add investment for trader.\\n\\n   ###### ![888.png](https://bafybeibixmvl5uy7yanoqd24ybpozioj3omynxxvmaqdpjdcs2bpfdph3y.ipfs.nftstorage.link/777.png)"}]}')}}]);